### Key Analysis Insights
- At step 1500 (collapse point), min_res=6 triggers TV350 budget to drop to 1 aligner
- Hub resources: carbon=6, oxygen=47 — huge imbalance causing budget collapse
- Aligner floor (TV469/v858/v865) prevents this specific failure mode
- RL agents (modular-lstm) are fundamentally more efficient at scramble/align cycles

